$ oradebug current_sql

`oradebug current_sql` gets the traced → development/databases/Oracle/architecture/session[session's] currently executed SQL statement:
code {
SYS> → development/databases/Oracle/tools/oradebug/setospid[oradebug setospid] 49091
SYS> oradebug current_sql
select … from …
code }

sa:
  → development/databases/Oracle/tools/oradebug
